item.title: CVE-2023-22816|2024-09-09T14:39:16.112Z -- western%20digital -- my%20cloud%20os%205
item.description: A post-authentication remote command injection vulnerability in a CGI file in Western Digital My Cloud OS 5 devices that could allow an attacker to build files with redirects and execute larger payloads. This issue affects My Cloud OS 5 devices: before 5.26.300.
